## Comandos
{% if language == "Python" %}
```bash
# Testes
python -m pytest tests/ -v

# Lint
ruff check .
ruff format .

# Type check
mypy src/
```
{% elif language == "Node.js" %}
```bash
# Testes
npx vitest run

# Lint
npx eslint .
npx prettier --check .

# Type check
npx tsc --noEmit
```
{% endif %}

